<item>
            <title>[PIG-3984] PigServer.shutdown remove the tez resource folder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3984</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3978&quot; title=&quot;Container reuse does not across PigServer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3978&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3978&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; make tez resource folder live across sessions. However, if PigServer.shutdown is called, tez resource folder will be removed and following job will fail. Bunch of tez unit test fail due to this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
